divs: sighting detailswhat prompted my contact with your organization is seeing a report on tv describing a craft very closely resembling one in my experience. in my case, there was an "element" involved that in my experience no other object, situation or activity could "generate" i would think that anyone who encountered this, well, craft for lack of a better word, would be able to describe this "element". to my knowledge, no witnesses have spoke of this, it may even be my own experience may be unique, possibly due to close proximity. anyway, it would help me considerably to hear someone credibly confirm what i would think would be a unmistakeable experience, in addition to a sighting. i am not referring in any way to abductions, tests, little gray or green creatures or any popular beliefs concerning unknown activities. anyway, i'd be willing to speak under confidential circumstances, and would prefer to speak with anyone who has encountered this craft (same general shape as illinois description, no lights) regards, [cms\tg\pid]
